<P>
I saw "The Cosby Show" episode about pregnancy and thought it was one of the 
funniest yet. I didn't think it was in poor taste at all. A man will never know 
what it's like to be pregnant and the way the show portrayed how a man might 
dream about it was absolutely hilarious although it looked more like a 
nightmare! 
</P>
<P>
Ellen Andersen, Sun Valley 
</P>
