<HEADLINE>
<P>
CRITICS' CHOICE: LODZ GHETTO: INSIDE A COMMUNITY UNDER SIEGE COMPILED AND 
EDITED BY ALAN ADELSON AND ROBERT LAPIDES (VIKING: $29.95; 526 PP.) 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Jonathan Kirsch 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Let anyone who still dares to deny that the Nazi genocide took place, let 
anyone who is still tempted to trivialize the suffering of 6 million Jewish 
men, women and childen, let anyone who allows himself the luxury of forgetting 
pick up a copy of 'Lodz Ghetto' and stare into the human face of the 
Holocaust." Jonathan Kirsch 
</P>
