</P>
<P>
Austria: 39 cents 
</P>
<P>
Sweden: 38 cents 
</P>
<P>
Netherlands: 36 cents 
</P>
<P>
France: 35 cents 
</P>
<P>
Belgium: 34 cents 
</P>
<P>
Canada: 32 cents 
</P>
<P>
U.K.: 32 cents 
</P>
<P>
Australia: 32 cents 
</P>
<P>
Switzerland: 31 cents 
</P>
<P>
United States: 25 cents 
</P>
<P>
Source: The Washington Post 
</P>
