<HEADLINE>
<P>
2 HOSTAGES FREED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BD Times Staff WriterPANAMA CITYPro-Noriega forces Saturday freed two American 
hostages here. 
</P>
<P>
They are Jon Meyersohn, a CBS News producer seized Wednesday at the Marriott 
Hotel, and American businessman Doug Mullen, a GTE executive who was captured 
along with Meyersohn. 
</P>
<P>
Meyersohn's disappearance had been a subject of rising concern. There had been 
no earlier reports of Mullen's captivity. 
</P>
