THIRD WORLD; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- IRAQ; AEROSPACE INDUSTRY -- THIRD WORLD; 
CHINA -- ARMS SALES -- SAUDI ARABIA; ISRAEL -- DEFENSE; DIAGNOSTIC TESTS; 
PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT; TRENDS 
</P>
