<P>
Wild Art 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA122489-0114 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 153061 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
December 24, 1989, Sunday, South Bay Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 1 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
1501 words 
