boosters in cheers for the 49ers. RICK CORRALES / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Allen's five years with the Rams (49-19-4) had plenty of high points, but he 
was left out of the huddle before his second firing in 1978. ; Photo, Allen at 
age 29, when he became Whittier College coach in 1951, and during his 71-28-1 
tenure with the Washington Redskins in the 1970s. 
</P>
