contract over "Coming to America," DOUGLAS R. BURROWS / For The Times; Photo, a 
movie starring comedian Eddie Murphy, shown in costume. JOHN SEAKWOOD / Los 
Angeles Times; Photo, Talk show host Arsenio Hall also starred in "Coming to 
America." LARRY BESSEL / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
