<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $30 when dream Traveler, the front horse 
in his parlay, ran out of the money. Pretender's Gold, the other half of the 
parlay, finished second. Bob, who started the meeting with a mythical $1,000 
bankroll, is now at $830.30. 
</P>
<P>
For today, Bob's bet is a $60 parlay from Ortega in the sixth to Stephen's 
Sooner in the seventh. 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Bankroll: $860.30 
</P>
<P>
