<SUBJECT>
<P>
MOTION PICTURES; MOTION PICTURE RATINGS; 1980S (DECADE); ACTORS; MOTION 
INDUSTRY -- UNITED STATES; MOTION PICTURE AUDIENCES; 1989 (YEAR) 
</P>
