</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
CONKLIN, GARY; FOOTBALL PLAYERS; COLLEGE ATHLETICS; UNIVERSITY OF WASHINGTON; 
FREEDOM BOWL (FOOTBALL GAME) 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
